  <brief_title>Preoperative Anxiety and Postoperative Pain in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of 2 Methods to Reduce Postoperative Pain in Children and a Comparison of 3 Methods of Preoperative Education Intervention to Reduce Anxiety in Children and Their Family</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
